						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the ruines of the Śiva temple near the village.</p>						

						<p>8th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription may be assigned to 8th century on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of a hero Koṟjrṉṟu the son <hi rend="italic">(maganṟu)</hi> of Ōbaḷi Muduḷa in a cattle field.</p>						

